1.
In the initial login interface, the user needs to enter the account and password to log in to the APP.
If the account and password are correct, the login is successful. Otherwise, the login failure is displayed.

2.
After successful login, users can see part of the course code and full name of the course.
Users can click on the corresponding course to see the review content of the course.
There is a "log out" button at the top of the login interface.
By clicking it, the user can log out and return to the initial login interface.

3.
Users can search for the corresponding course code and then click on the instance to see the comments.
After entering the corresponding course comment area, users can also filter comments by searching for keywords or time.